    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Dispose indeed happens _after_ the widget and component is unmounted, to prevent it being called twice during strict mode. React Router should be synchronisable with the history router directly, similar to the next integration: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/blob/master/packages/react-instantsearch-router-nextjs/src/index.ts#L99-L175, have you tried that?",
